      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 is an FDA-recognized, commercially validated solver operating under ISO 9001-compliant quality management. Input files were version-controlled and archived. QA level 2 is commensurate with model risk level 3 under medium-consequence COU."
