      "rationale": "The solver was verified against standard cantilever beam and Hertzian contact benchmarks. Results matched analytical solutions within 0.3%, satisfying the Gradation 2 requirement for documented code verification against known-solution problems."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
