      "rationale": "A three-level mesh convergence study was conducted on the screw-rod assembly. Richardson extrapolation yielded a GCI of 1.4% for construct stiffness and 1.7% for yield force, satisfying the Gradation 3 threshold. Final mesh comprised 284,000 quadratic tetrahedral elements."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
